# VERA Security & Backup Strategy Exclusions
# Defined in backup.md

# 1. Database files & logs
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# 2. Running Logs
*.log

# 3. Source Data & Documents
*.csv
*.pdf

# 4. Historical Backups
backups/
*.bak*
*.backup*
*.tar.gz
*.zip
*.csv.*
*.db.*

# 5. Environment & Caches
.venv/
venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/

# 6. System & Others
.DS_Store
.streamlit/secrets.toml
outputs/
output_V4/
proceeded/

# 7. Note on GitHub commits (As per strategy):
# Ensure only source code (*.py), configs, and docs (*.md) are committed.
